Well done to all players. We hope @HerefordFC fans will join us in saying well done when the players are presented at half time on Saturday!

U18 Player of the Month

Tom Gameson

Continued overall improvement. Shown great commitment & behaviour & very supportive to other players!

U16 Player of the Month

Cam Godsall

Cam has not missed any training or games & has played in several position & played consistently well!

U15 Player of the Month

Matt McLeod

Outstanding commitment & attitude in training. Hard-working player determined to learn & be successful

U14 Player of the Month

Toby King 

Toby has shown outstanding commitment & attitude in training & has contributed to many goals this month

U13 Player of the Month

Tom Hassan

Tom's commitment & application to training has been great. He has developed well in a new position.

U12 Player of the Month

Tim Honey

Tim's attitude in training & games has been excellent. Tim has shown great leadership skills. Well done!
